{"tid":1320414,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係香港打工有咩前境？","createTime":"2019-07-15T11:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:31:41.000Z","uid":12555,"like":33,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b6972a64c52c3908c27ec0544cf16b7b6ed476","tid":1320414,"uid":12555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"自己係大學畢咗業幾年，<br />\n發現原來你讀啲咩同你做啲咩係無關。<br />\n<br />\n因為你讀同做係兩回事，<br />\n唔係專科（護士、工程、醫生、律師...）<br />\n一畢業出嚟都只係揸緊13、14k...<br />\n打咗兩年工出嚟跳槽，<br />\n發現所有咩officer都係16k左右...<br />\n<br />\n究竟香港有咩工可以去到20k以上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府工又爭崩頭，<br />\n私人市場又要低人工叫你做好撚多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：社科畢業（非社工系）<br />\n<br />\n待業揸兜中，奉勤各位準大學生，<br />\n想入社科，但唔係Social Work都唔好讀..."},{"pid":"aa16603b1e231fe1aae84c490fbcbdc3c2228c26","tid":1320414,"uid":108236,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:30:26.000Z","msg":"工程係做狗方面都算係專業既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851ad5bfa53ecb8480121bc9691f6d4925423d70","tid":1320414,"uid":71508,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"沒有廢科，只有廢人<br />\n                                   By魯迅"},{"pid":"7811be7297fac9e442c85989ec350817a4500c7a","tid":1320414,"uid":35315,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"讀書想搵錢但唔讀專科已經係自我矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ca379a17981d14a7893b8e6f867eb59846ae7c","tid":1320414,"uid":246764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:43:15.000Z","msg":"做做下就會有，除非無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ag